description:
Cuteness is waiting for you. 

The zulily app is your on-the-go source for all things adorable. Our featured brands change every day, so you never know exactly what you'll find for you and your little one. But you can be sure it's worth a look. We're obsessed with making you smile. 

The zulily app offers quick, free access to sweet style 
• Something special every day
• Open at 6am PST 
• Boutique brands at up to 90% off retail prices 
• See what's coming soon and set alarms
• Invite new members and earn credit
• Share finds with your friends

Not a zulily member yet? No problem! It's free and you can join from the app. Take a peek into our whimsical world. See what you see. We think you'll love it!

By signing in to our app, you agree to the zulily Terms and Conditions & our Privacy Practices
http://www.zulily.com/terms-conditions
http://www.zulily.com/privacy-practices
releaseNotes:
We want the zulily app to feel as fresh as the great products you'll find on it, so we're bringing you an app update every week! It's simple: we're listening to what you want, and bringing it to you as fast as we can. We're obsessed with creating the best mobile shopping experience possible, so give us your feedback -- we're listening.

Always want the latest version without having to check for updates? If you're running iOS7 or higher on your device, you can set your app up to automatically download our updates whenever they're ready to go. To turn on automatic updating, go to Settings > iTunes & App Store > Automatic Downloads. Thanks for shopping with us!
